opened up, and suddenly I

00:36:14.080 --> 00:36:16.630 align:middle line:90%
was in a very ecstatic state.

00:36:16.630 --> 00:36:19.510 align:middle line:84%
And I realized, you cannot
find meaning in life using

00:36:19.510 --> 00:36:20.950 align:middle line:90%
your reason.

00:36:20.950 --> 00:36:23.290 align:middle line:84%
This was a very important
first experience.

00:36:23.290 --> 00:36:28.450 align:middle line:84%
It suddenly showed me whole
new potentials of psychedelics.

00:36:28.450 --> 00:36:31.050 align:middle line:90%


00:36:31.050 --> 00:36:34.180 align:middle line:84%
>> Through his own experiences
and those of his patients,

00:36:34.180 --> 00:36:37.260 align:middle line:84%
