00:37:24.860 --> 00:37:26.780 align:middle line:90%
fundamental assumptions.

00:37:26.780 --> 00:37:29.150 align:middle line:84%
And I had a very
personal experience

00:37:29.150 --> 00:37:30.740 align:middle line:90%
that made it even worse.

00:37:30.740 --> 00:37:34.970 align:middle line:84%
I went as a second year student
