00:37:34.970 --> 00:37:35.900 align:middle line:90%
Laufberger.

00:37:35.900 --> 00:37:39.560 align:middle line:84%
And I asked, how far
back does our memory go?

00:37:39.560 --> 00:37:42.470 align:middle line:84%
Can we, for example,
relive our birth?

00:37:42.470 --> 00:37:45.350 align:middle line:84%
And he looked at me like
