00:37:55.370 --> 00:37:58.010 align:middle line:84%
So I had that kind
of additional memory,

00:37:58.010 --> 00:38:01.020 align:middle line:84%
like this was really
stupid to think

00:38:01.020 --> 00:38:02.930 align:middle line:84%
that you could
relive your birth,

00:38:02.930 --> 00:38:05.780 align:middle line:84%
even if it seems
very convincing.

00:38:05.780 --> 00:38:08.240 align:middle line:84%
But then of course, if
