00:38:08.240 --> 00:38:11.210 align:middle line:84%
and had a few more
experiences myself,

00:38:11.210 --> 00:38:16.850 align:middle line:84%
I realized that this
edifice of psychiatry

00:38:16.850 --> 00:38:20.660 align:middle line:84%
