00:39:06.340 --> 00:39:09.110 align:middle line:84%
We were living in the
suburbs outside of Paris,

00:39:09.110 --> 00:39:12.850 align:middle line:84%
and I was four months
pregnant with my son, Oscar.

00:39:12.850 --> 00:39:15.730 align:middle line:84%
The first shot missed my
head by about 12 inches,

00:39:15.730 --> 00:39:19.240 align:middle line:84%
