00:39:22.240 --> 00:39:25.420 align:middle line:84%
I'd wake up at night
reliving the experience

00:39:25.420 --> 00:39:29.590 align:middle line:84%
and imagining
where I would hide.

00:39:29.590 --> 00:39:32.710 align:middle line:84%
Later, when Oscar was old
