00:46:42.655 --> 00:46:45.660 align:middle line:90%


00:46:45.660 --> 00:46:48.540 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the great
contributions of Stan's work is

00:46:48.540 --> 00:46:51.450 align:middle line:84%
